hymnContent.content:
Nzamurora mu maso ye,
Turi kumwe mw' ijuru;
Meny' uk' ubwiza bwe busa;
Nzamusingiz' iteka.

Igisambo ku musaraba, Kiyarabutswe cyarihannye;
Nanjye mbwiriza nkwizigire, Noye kujya ncumura;
Ibyaha mbicikeho rwose, Noye kujya nkugomera;
Nanjye mbwiriza nkwizigire, Noye kujya ncumura.

Amaraso yaw' atunganye, Ahoran' imbaraga nyinshi;
Niyo wacunguj' itorero, Aritsembamw' ibyaha;
Ryaganjij' imbaraga yabyo. Ryarabirokotse rwose.
Niyo wacunguj' itorero, Yaritsembyemw' ibyaha.

Shaka gutungana, Jy' uhor' usenga;
Bana n' Uwiteka, Ujy' umwumvira;
Jy' ukund' Abakristo, Fash' abarembye;
Ntuhuge na hato, Gushak' ihirwe.

Shaka gutungana, Hagomye benshi;
Horana na Yesu, Mu rwiherero.
N' umwitegereza, Uzaba nka we;
Bose bazamenya, K' umeze nka we.

Mur' iyi si byose birashira,
Nta munezer' uhaba na hato;
Nta kidapfa, nta kidahinduka;
Wow' udahinyuka, ungumane.

N' ungumana, nta mubisha ntinya;
Ishavu rizab' umunezero;
Imbori z' urupfu zizashira;
Ntabwo ntazanesha n' ungumana.

Ngah' umuns' urakuze, Burije turuhuke;
Kand' ubw' imuri z' ijoro zaka turamy' Uwiteka,
Twebwe twese.

Mwami nyir' ubugingo, Terany' abagushaka;
Buzuze bos' urukundo, Ubagir' ubwoko bwawe,
Bakuramye.

Umwijima n' ugwira, Dukingir' imbabazi;
Tukwegerez' imitima, Hirya y' ubwiza bw' ijuru,
Ngo duhirwe.

Umpagarik' umunsi n' ijoro;
Ntabwo nabaho tutari kumwe;
Ungumane mu makuba,
Kuko ntinya gupf' utahari.

Nikomeze ku Rutare,
Nahw' ahandi n' umusenyi;
Nahw' ahandi n' umusenyi.

Nta kitubabaza, Nta shavu tugira;
Niw' uduhembur' imbu zose;
Nta bworo n' isari, Nta n' umubabaro;
Tuzahirwa ni tumwizera.

Hafi y' iwacu, Hafi yaho;
Ubu ngeze hafi y' iwacu,
Ngiye gusohorayo.

Mpimbaze, mpimbaze; Yesu wankijij' ibyaha.
Anyigisha kumuramya, Ngo nezerw' iminsi yose;
Mpimbaze, mpimbaze Yesu wankijij' ibyaha.

Nkunda kwogez' amagambo, Y' ubwami bwo mw' ijuru;
Ya Yesu n' ishimwe rye, Ya Yesu n' urukundo rwe.
Niyo nkunda kwogeza, Kuko nzi kw' ar' ukuri;
Niy' amp' ibyo nifuza, Nta handi mbibona.

Nkunda kwogez' amagambo, Arut' ibintu byose;
Ahebuz' umurimbo; N' ibyo turigira byose,
Niyo nkunda kwogeza. Yangiriy' umumaro;
Simpwema kuyarata, Ngw abakize namwe.

Nkunda kwogez' amagambo, Nkomeze njye nyavuga;
Aranogera cyane, Kukw' ambwiriz' iby' ijuru;
Niyo nkunda kwogeza, Nyabwir' abatayazi,
Bameny' ako gakiza, Kava mu nzandiko.

Nsingiz' Imana Rurema, Yaremy' imisozi;
Yadendej' inyanja zose, Yahanits' ijuru;
Nsingiz' iyahay' izuba, Kumurika mu munsi.
Ih' ukwezi kubonesha, N' inyenyer' umucyo.

S. na A.:

Uyu munsi, uyu munsi ;
Yes' araguhamagaran' imbabazi ze.

T. na B.:

Uyu munsi, none, none;
Uyu munsi, none, none;
Yesu Yes' Umwami ni w'
Uguhamagaran' imbabazi ze.

Ubyarw' ubwa kabiri (rwose);
Ubyarw' ubwa kabiri (rwose);
N' ukuri, n' ukuri, ndakubwir' ubu
Kw' aribw' uzarama (rwose).

Nahabiye kure, nd' akahebwe;
Nahabiye kure y' iwacu.
Nyakira none, maz' ungez' iwacu;
Ngwin' unyirokorere.

Sop :

Twubake kuri we, Twubake kuri we;
Twubake ku Rutare rw' iteka,
Nirwo Yes' Umwami.

A.T.B :

Twubake kuri we, Niwe Rutare;
Twubake kuri we, Niwe Rutare;
Twubake ku Rutare rw' iteka,
Nirwo Yes' Umwami.

Mbwira n' ibyo mu butayu, N' iminsi yahamaze;
N' uburyo yageragejwe, Agatsind' ibishuko;
Mbwira n' iby' imirimo ye, Vug' uko yababajwe;
Agahemurwa bamwanze, Agahinyurwa nk' impabe.

Nzasingiz' urukundo rwe;
Mpimbaze, Yaramfiriye,
Ashaka kumbeshaho;
Nzahora muhimbaza.

Nyigiza hafi, mbane nawe; Nta cyandutira kubana nawe.
Ngumisha mu gituza cyawe; Mpisha nibere mu buhungiro;
Mpisha nibere mu buhungiro.

Nyigiza hafi, ntacyo mfite; Ntacyo nzanyehw' ituro ry' Umwami,
Kerets' umutim' ushavuye; Mpa kuhagizw' amaraso yawe;
Mpa kuhagizw' amaraso yawe.

Nyigiza hafi, Mwami wanjye; Nishimiye gucika ku byaha.
Ndeke kwikuza n' ubwibone; Umpe Yes' Umwami wambambiwe;
Umpe Yes' Umwami wambambiwe.

Nyigiza hafi, ngihumeka; Kugez' ubwo nzager' i Budapfa;
Maze mu bihe bidashira, Nzibere hafi y' Umwami wanjye;
Nzibere hafi y' Umwami wanjye.

Yesu gusa, niw' ukwiriy' ikuzo;
Naho jyewe, ntacyo ndi cyo rwose;
Sinkwiriye kub' ari jyew' uratwa;
Yesu gusa, niw' uzajy' uvugwa.

Yesu gusa, niw' umar' agahinda;
Naho jyewe nd' uwo gushavura.
Sinshobora kwikorer' ibindushya;
Naho Yesu nta kimushengura.

Yesu gusa, ab' ari we wogezwa;
Sinkwiriye kwiratan' ibyanjye.
Yesu gusa, niw' uzambonekamo;
Kugez' ubwo nzahinduka nka we.

Yesu gusa niw' umar' ubukene;
Niwe gusa nkesh' ibyanjye byose.
Yesu gusa, niw' undutira byose;
Yesu Mwami twibanir' iteka.

Irankunda, irankunda;
Nzi ko nanjy' inkunda;
Kukw' ikund' utuntu duto,
Nzi ko nanjy' inkunda.

Wateranye natwe, mu bindi bihe, Ariko na n' ubu turakwifuza.
Ngwino, Mubyeyi mwiza, Turakwinginze;
Twumvir' utwemere, Duhirwe nawe.

Wakir' indirimbo z' ishimwe ryacu, Uduhe gusenga tubyitayeho.
Twongerere kwizera, No kwiringira;
Dukundane rwose, Dushyire hamwe.

Ndusheho gusa nawe, Yesu Mukiza wanjye;
Nyuzuz' ubugwaneza, Mp' urukundo ruhebuje.
Ndusheho kumera nkawe, Aho ngenda hose, Mwami;
Ndiyoroheje rwose, Mwami njye ngukurikiza.

Nib' irind' icyanira, Ikamenya n' igishwi;
Sinshidikanya rwose, Nanjy' ihor' inyitayeho.
Izanyigisha kwitonda, Imbabarir' amafuti;
Ndiyoroheje rwose, Mwami njye ngukurikiza.

Ndusheho gusa nawe, Ndusheh' uko bukeye;
Nyigiza hafi yawe, Ahw' amahor' adashira.
Uhor' umpindura mushya, Kubw' urukund' ungirira;
Ndiyoroheje rwose, Mwami njye ngukurikiza.

Ntabwo nahangara kugenda, Ntari kumwe nawe, Mukiza;
Nagoswe n' abanz' igihumbi; Dor' imitegw' intaye hagati.
Burije rwose, ntihabona, Nkomeze njyane nawe, Mwami.

Ninguma mu maboko yawe, Sinzaba ncyitaye ku by' isi;
Nta kindi nziratana rwose, Keretse wa musaraba wawe,
Ngez' ubwo nzager' i Siyoni, Nkomeze njyane nawe, Mwami.

Nyuhagiz' amaraso yawe ( nere rwose );
Maz' anyezehw' inenge yose ( nere rwose );
Ibyanjye byose ndabikweguriye, None n' iteka ryose.

Nabony' inshut' ihebuje! Yankunze ntarabaho;
Yanyiyegereshej' ineza, N' urukundo rw' iteka,
Bituma dushyikirana, Ubudatandukana;
Kuko nd' uwe nawe n' uwanjye, Ibihe bidashira.

Mb' uwawe ( Mwami ) ;
Mb' uwawe ( Mwami ) ;
Niyo migambi yanjye ;
Mb' uwawe ( Mwami ) ;
Mb' uwawe ( Mwami ) ;
Mb' uwawe Mwami, None.

Udusezeresh' umugisha wawe; Mwam' utwuzuz' amahoro;
Urukundo rwawe rudusabemo, Tubone kunesha rwose.
Ngwin' uduhembure, Ngwin' uduhembure;
Tukiri mur' iyi si y' igomero.

Tuguhay' ishimwe no kukuramya, Kubw' ubutumwa bw' imvaho,
Bwagukomotseho bukadukiza, Bunyur' imitima yacu;
Tubushikamemo, Tubushikamemo;
Tugundir' ukuri, Tudacogora.

Mbeshwaho n' imbabazi zawe nyinshi, None ndakwiyeguriye.
Ngwin' uduhumurish' impuhwe zawe, Duhore turwan' ishyaka;
Tuzager' i wawe, Tuzager' iwawe;
Tukubone nta kidukingirije.

Nzamura maze nger' aho wangeneye,
Mwami wanjye; Ku rugero rusumbyeho;
Mwami mfasha ngo ndusheho.

Ntushak' urwitwazo urahamagawe;
Dor' aho wangiye, Noneho witabe.
Imirim' ireze, Hagumy' abakozi;
Ngwin' umukorere; Uzagororerwa.

Ndakwiyeguriy' ubu, Ez' ibyaha byanjye;
Ngaragareh' ubwiza bwawe buhebuje.
Ngir' umutim' utuje, Ne guteraganwa;
Niyoroshye nganduke, Ngo nkoreshwe nawe.

S. na A :

Gendera mu mucyo, Gendera mu mucyo;
Gendera mu mucyo, Mu mucyo waka w' Imana.

T. na B. :

Gendera mu mucy' utangaje w' Imana;
Gendera mu mucy' utangaje w' Imana;
Gendera mu mucy' utangaje w' Imana;
Mu mucyo waka w' Imana;
